{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I started my journey 30 years ago."},{"time":3000,"text":"And I worked in mines. And I realized that"},{"time":5000,"text":"this was a world unseen."},{"time":7000,"text":"And I wanted, through color and large format cameras"},{"time":9000,"text":"and very large prints,"},{"time":11000,"text":"to make a body of work that somehow"},{"time":13000,"text":"became symbols of our"},{"time":16000,"text":"use of the landscape,"},{"time":18000,"text":"how we use the land."},{"time":20000,"text":"And to me this was"},{"time":22000,"text":"a key component that somehow, through this medium of photography,"},{"time":25000,"text":"which allows us to contemplate these landscapes,"},{"time":28000,"text":"that I thought photography was perfectly suited"},{"time":31000,"text":"to doing this type of work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"And after 17 years of photographing large industrial landscapes,"},{"time":37000,"text":"it occurred to me that"},{"time":39000,"text":"oil is underpinning the scale and speed."},{"time":41000,"text":"Because that is what has changed,"},{"time":43000,"text":"is the speed at which we're taking all our resources."},{"time":46000,"text":"And so then I went out to develop a whole series"},{"time":48000,"text":"on the landscape of oil."},{"time":50000,"text":"And what I want to do is to kind of map an arc"},{"time":55000,"text":"that there is extraction, where we're taking it from the ground,"},{"time":58000,"text":"refinement. And that's one chapter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"The other chapter that I wanted to look at was"},{"time":62000,"text":"how we use it -- our cities,"},{"time":64000,"text":"our cars, our motorcultures,"},{"time":66000,"text":"where people gather around the vehicle"},{"time":70000,"text":"as a celebration."},{"time":72000,"text":"And then the third one is this idea of the end of oil,"},{"time":74000,"text":"this entropic end,"},{"time":76000,"text":"where all of our parts of cars, our tires,"},{"time":79000,"text":"oil filters,"},{"time":81000,"text":"helicopters, planes --"},{"time":83000,"text":"where are the landscapes where all of that stuff ends up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"And to me, again, photography was"},{"time":88000,"text":"a way in which I could explore and research the world,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and find those places."},{"time":93000,"text":"And another idea that I had as well,"},{"time":95000,"text":"that was brought forward by an ecologist --"},{"time":99000,"text":"he basically did a calculation where"},{"time":102000,"text":"he took one liter of gas and said,"},{"time":104000,"text":"well, how much carbon it would take, and how much organic material?"},{"time":108000,"text":"It was 23 metric tons for one liter."},{"time":111000,"text":"So whenever I fill up my gas,"},{"time":113000,"text":"I think of that liter, and how much carbon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"And I know that oil comes from the ocean and phytoplankton,"},{"time":118000,"text":"but he did the calculations for our Earth"},{"time":121000,"text":"and what it had to do to produce that amount of energy."},{"time":123000,"text":"From the photosynthetic growth,"},{"time":125000,"text":"it would take 500 years of that growth"},{"time":128000,"text":"to produce what we use, the 30 billion barrels we use per year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"And that also brought me to the fact that"},{"time":135000,"text":"this poses such a risk to our society."},{"time":138000,"text":"Looking at 30 billion per year,"},{"time":143000,"text":"we look at our two largest suppliers,"},{"time":145000,"text":"Saudi Arabia and now Canada, with its dirty oil."},{"time":147000,"text":"And together they only form about 15 years of supply."},{"time":151000,"text":"The whole world, at 1.2 trillion estimated reserves,"},{"time":154000,"text":"only gives us about 45 years."},{"time":156000,"text":"So, it's not a question of if, but a question of when"},{"time":159000,"text":"peak oil will come upon us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"So, to me, using photography --"},{"time":163000,"text":"and I feel that all of us need to now begin to really"},{"time":166000,"text":"take the task of using our talents,"},{"time":168000,"text":"our ways of thinking,"},{"time":171000,"text":"to begin to deal with what I think is probably"},{"time":173000,"text":"one of the most challenging issues of our time,"},{"time":176000,"text":"how to deal with our energy crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"And I would like to say that, on the other side of it,"},{"time":180000,"text":"30, 40 years from now, the children that I have,"},{"time":182000,"text":"I can look at them and say, \"We did everything"},{"time":184000,"text":"we possibly, humanly could do,"},{"time":187000,"text":"to begin to mitigate this,"},{"time":190000,"text":"what I feel is one of the most important and critical"},{"time":192000,"text":"moments in our time. Thank you."},{"time":195000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}